# K7RKScan.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 

### Description

Driver can be used to load unsigned drivers
- **UUID**: 9f88300d-e607-4e50-8626-fd799439e049
- **Created**: 2025-09-18
- **Author**: Michael Haag

{{< button "https://github.com/magicsword-io/LOLDrivers/raw/main/drivers/d690827cdb58631444dfd8607d99b9c1.bin" "Download" >}}{{< button "https://www.magicsword.io/premium" "Block" "red" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create K7RKScan.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\K7RKScan.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start K7RKScan.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
